          <p style="margin-top: 2em;">
          OxTran welcomes contributions from all within the Oxford area. It is moderated by Gordon Stokes and Karen Lucas of the TSU.  Please send contributions and suggestions to <a href="mailto:oxtran@tsu.ox.ac.uk">oxtran@tsu.ox.ac.uk</a>
          </p>
